{"title":"Ornot gets to Work w/ new Bibs & Lightweight Summer Jerseys","link":"https://bikerumor.com/ornot-work-jersey-bibshorts/","date":1689604295000,"content":"<p>Catering to those who want a well-executed fit and finish but without the bells and whistles (and price tag) of high end cycling kits, the new Ornot <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=23377&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fproducts%2Flightweight-work-jersey-burgundy\" target=\"_blank\">Lightweight Summer Jersey</a> and <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=23377&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fproducts%2Fwork-bib-short-slate\" target=\"_blank\">Work Bibshorts</a> fit the bill for riders looking to beat the heat.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The new jerseys, also part of their new “Work” series, are a minimalist design with three pockets and a breathable, Italian-milled open-knit mesh. They use a YKK zipper and are constructed of 100% Bluesign-approved recycled polyester, equivalent to about 8 plastic water bottles per jersey.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1201\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2.jpg\" alt=\"ornot work lightweight summer jerseys shown on two riders\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-2-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Work jersey comes in Stone Blue, Burgundy, and Fog colors in both <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=23377&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fproducts%2Flightweight-work-jersey-burgundy\" target=\"_blank\">men’s</a> and <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=23377&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fproducts%2Fwomens-lightweight-work-jersey-burgundy\" target=\"_blank\">women’s</a> versions.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1799\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1.jpg\" alt=\"women's ornot work lightweight summer jerseys shown on rider\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1.jpg 1200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1-200x300.jpg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1-80x120.jpg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1-768x1151.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-1-1025x1536.jpg 1025w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1201\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3.jpg\" alt=\"men's ornot work lightweight summer jerseys shown on rider\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3.jpg 1800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3-297x198.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3-800x534.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3-120x80.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-lightweight-work-jersey-3-720x480.jpg 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>All have reflective details on the back and retail for $98 each.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-scaled.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"779\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"ornot men's work bibshorts\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-297x90.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-800x243.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-120x37.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-768x234.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-1536x467.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/ornot-work-bibshorts-4-2048x623.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>To go with them, the new Work bibshorts (men’s only for now) have a single cargo pocket on the right side and an endurance chamois on the inside for all-day riding. These, too, are made with Bluesign-approved fabric and eco-friendly processes.</p>\n\n\n\n<p> They have a one-piece strap with high waistband front and rear. They have a wide silicone-free leg gripper and offer 35 UPF sun protection. MSRP is <strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=23377&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2Fproducts%2Fwork-bib-short-slate\" target=\"_blank\">$148</a></strong>, available now in Black and Slate in sizes XS through XXL.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=23377&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ornotbike.com%2F\">OrnotBike.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/ornot-work-jersey-bibshorts/\">Ornot gets to Work w/ new Bibs &amp; Lightweight Summer Jerseys</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"98e43c0925213e074b71a46011fbab5896446ed92b9d78e47a285e56cd01c1a4","category":"Cycling"}